TO SHARE FILES

plorkserv name directory [port]
for example:
  $ cd mypiece
  $ plorkserv mypiece .

TO GET FILES

plorkup name
for example:
  $ cd mypiece
  $ plorkup mypiece


-------
Only Tom cares about what's below this line.

install to a custom gem repository:
  gem install [gem] --install-dir=/path/to/gems

use the repository to read gems:
  export GEM_PATH=/path/to/gems
